OL,3,CGolders Green victim tells ITV News he
OL,4,Cholds the government responsible
OL,6,FWatch ITV News UK Editor Paul Brand
OL,7,Fspeaking to Golders Green stabbing
OL,8,Fvictim Shilome Rand
OL,10,FA victim of the suspected terror
OL,11,Fattack in Golders Green has told ITV
OL,12,FNews that the government is "not doing
OL,13,Fits job" in protecting the Jewish
OL,14,Fcommunity and that it is a "miracle"
OL,15,Fhe is alive.
OL,17,FShilome Rand, 34, is being treated in
OL,18,Fhospital for wounds to the chest after
OL,19,Fhe was stabbed as he was leaving his
OL,20,Fsynagogue on Wednesday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
