OL,3,CGolders Green victim tells ITV News he
OL,4,Cholds the government responsible
OL,6,FHe said he had been inundated with
OL,7,Fmessages since his identity, as one of
OL,8,Fthe two victims of the attack, was
OL,9,Frevealed in dramatic video of the
OL,10,Fattack.
OL,12,F"People are really concerned, people
OL,13,Fare afraid, people are uncomfortable
OL,14,Fwalking in the street, people are
OL,15,Fblaming obviously the government for
OL,16,Fnot doing anything about what's going
OL,17,Fon," he told ITV News UK Editor Paul
OL,18,FBrand.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
