CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777514612
OL,3,CGolders Green victim tells ITV News he
OL,4,Cholds the government responsible
OL,6,F"It's for the past few months really
OL,7,Fthat our community is suffering from
OL,8,Fthese type of attacks. And now it's
OL,9,Fgoing on and trying to take people's
OL,10,Flives and it's really terrible."
OL,12,FAsked whether he also felt let down by
OL,13,Fthe government, Shilome said
OL,14,F"definitely".
OL,16,FHe added: "The government, they are
OL,17,Fthe ones that are able to take care of
OL,18,Fthe problems. And they are not doing
OL,19,Ftheir job."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
