OL,3,CGolders Green victim tells ITV News he
OL,4,Cholds the government responsible
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FShilome told ITV News that he was
OL,12,Fheading back to his car, after doing
OL,13,Fhis studies at the synagogue, when the
OL,14,Fsuspect came running towards him.
OL,16,FHe was not immediately aware of the
OL,17,Fimminent threat, but as the victim
OL,18,Flaunched his attack, Shilome realised
OL,19,Fhis life was in danger.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
