OL,3,CGolders Green victim tells ITV News he
OL,4,Cholds the government responsible
OL,6,F"He looked angry, he looked angry," he
OL,7,Ftold ITV News. "You could feel it in
OL,8,Fhis facial expressions, it was like he
OL,9,Fwas out to get me."
OL,11,FShilome said he was initially told
OL,12,Fthat he would need emergency surgery,
OL,13,Fbut that his wound was not as bad as
OL,14,Ffirst feared.
OL,16,F"Thanks to God that I am recovering,
OL,17,Fand the wound isn't so bad as they
OL,18,Finitially thought," he said.
OL,20,FHe said he was lucky to be alive.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
