OL,3,CGolders Green victim tells ITV News he
OL,4,Cholds the government responsible
OL,6,F"I am here and I can talk, and it's
OL,7,Freally a miracle that has happened to
OL,8,Fme today," he told ITV News.
OL,10,FA second man who has been named as
OL,11,FMoshe Shine, aged 76, was attacked at
OL,12,Fa bus stop and also admitted to
OL,13,Fhospital.
OL,15,FITV News understands Mr Shine is in a
OL,16,Fserious but stable condition.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
